The paper discusses the use of autonomous aerial vehicles (UAVs) for delivering goods, which falls under the category of multi-agent systems (cs.MA) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses job selection policies, which involves decision-making and optimization, falling under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the paper introduces a methodological approach for decision-making support, which involves computational methods and machine learning, falling under the category of machine learning (cs.LG).
